title: Quercus pentacycla
text:
Quercus pentacycla is an uncommon Asian species of tree in the <a href="Fagaceae">beech family</a>. It has been found only in the Province of <a href="Yunnan">Yunnan</a> in southwestern China.
"Quercus pentacycla" is a tree up to 15 meters tall. Twigs are grayish brown. Leaves can be as much as 14 cm long.
